Installation

For firmware dev environment:

- Install Arduino IDE: http://arduino.cc/en/Main/Software
- Install TeensyDuino: http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/td_download.html
    - Disable driver signing if needed
- Copy Firmware\Teensy\libraries to <Arduino>\libraries

For software dev environment only:

- Install just the serial driver (part of TeensyDuino): http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/serial_install.exe
- Copy Firmware\Teensy\libraries to <Arduino>\libraries